{"tid":779924,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"上次去大鴻輝打邊爐搭緊𨋢 有幾個細路係到跳跳紮","createTime":"2018-08-14T18:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T05:01:43.000Z","uid":11598,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ed6d3e8182be84e434265effde5b3c2040416bb7","tid":779924,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T18:39:56.000Z","msg":"佢哋跳得好撚開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲老豆老母仲有講有笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後我同行幾個死肥仔就跟住一齊跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跳到部𨋢震咗幾下<br />\n班家長塊面嚇到青過青瓜  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲鬧鳩我哋會搞到困𨋢<br />\n我哋就笑笑口咁講唔好意思<br />\n我哋無家教<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1007e8c298d51cbed181f2e1173e9103b64fc4e7","tid":779924,"uid":22012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T18:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39a6b60d556bed9302b68d78f83f5ad3f418920","tid":779924,"uid":70201,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T18:42:15.000Z","msg":"係我未睇過呢篇潮文 定係你1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你係咪其中一個肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf7ef6a0713dfc51a2e60300f75bc99adafa329","tid":779924,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a39a6b60d556bed9302b68d78f83f5ad3f418920","tid":779924,"uid":70201,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"c